site_name: Land comprised within the Deveopment of Pudding Mill LaneQueen Elizabeth ParkLondon
application_type_full: Outline planning permission: All matters reserved
description: Outline application for the development at Pudding Mill Lane within Queen Elizabeth Olympic Park with all matters reserved for future determination comprising residential use (Use Class C3) including private amenity spaces; commercial, business and service uses (Use Class E); and local community use (Use Class F2); means of access; additional areas to provide associated plant, storage, circulation, servicing, car parking and cycle parking; landscaping including laying out of open space with provision for natural habitats and play space and all other supporting infrastructure works, structures and facilities
